            "introduction": {
              "introduction": "　A sniper who attacks faster after each shot.\n\n　She specializes in intercepting targets from a stationary position. While staying out of enemy attacks, she provides suppressing fire to create a safe environment for allies.\n　Careful and devoted, she always defends her position once given the order. There is a famous story that the enemy mistook her for dead because she stayed still even after getting shot.\n　Despite her cold and quiet looks, she is notorious for being a disciplinarian who keeps nagging at her comrades.　"
